job.title: JKSSB Jr. Asst., Stock Asst. Recruitment 2021 – Apply Online for 329 vacancies in Jammu and Kashmir
job.body:
Total vacancies:329

Name of the Vacancies:

  • Junior Assistant, Veterinary Pharmacist, Electrician, Junior Stenographer, Junior Grader, Rakhoverseer, Stock Assistant 

Description

Latest Central Government Jobs for Graduates has been published by J&K Services Selection Board for Junior Assistant vacancies in Jammu and Kashmir. If you are searching for a government job in Jammu and Kashmir then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies of Junior Assistant, from 04-08-2021, and till 06-09-2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in Jammu and Kashmir and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.

Application fee:

  • The mode of application is Online
  • No information about application fee

Educational qualification:

  • To apply for a Junior Assistant in JKSSB, your Graduation must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates:

  •  The starting date to apply in these posts is 04-08-2021
  •  The last date to apply in these posts is 06-09-2021

Age Limit Criteria:

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 35  years old. 

JKSSB Junior Assistant Pay Scale:

  • According to the information given by the Central Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is as per norms

Detailed Vacancies:

How to apply for JKSSB Jr Asst., Stock Asst. Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the Junior Assistant. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of JKSSB and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by JKSSB
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.

Download Official notification pdf.
